                    services in Texas in alignment with the state-wide Behavioral Health Strategic Plan.</p>

                <p>Each of the two statewide research networks is focused on a specific topic area pertinent to
                    advancing the delivery of child and adolescent mental health services. The networks are the:
                </p>

